      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 395°F/ Gas 6</p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a matching lid with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>focaccia </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until warmed through</p>",
